        <li>By mobile number. The actions are the same as in the first method, but after opening the registration window, go to the tab "By phone number" at the top. Then enter the number and currency. On the specified number will come a password (it will be possible to change it in the user's personal account), and you will use the number for login.</li>
        <li>By e-mail. Click on the tab with this name in the registration window. This option implies entering the country, region, city, name, surname, e-mail address, and number. Using other methods, you will also enter all this data for verification, but not immediately. Also, in the case of an e-mail, you have to create your own password. There will be an e-mail with a link to follow.</li>
