<div class="heads blue">
    <h2>‚Äã‚ÄãThe main types of betting at 1xBet and their features</h2>
</div>
<div class="callout">
    <p>Let us briefly consider what to bet on:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><b>A single bet</b> (1–•2) ‚Äìthe simplest type of bets, choose victory of the first, second-team/player or a draw, if it is possible in the selected match;</li>
        <li><b>total</b> (TB, TM) ‚Äì bet on the number of any indicators, for example, in soccer it can be goals, corner kicks, penalties, in tennis games, sets, and so on (choose whether the actual value will be more or less than that shown in the proposition bets;</li>
        <li><b>handicap</b> ‚Äìa bet that the team/player will win by a margin greater than the specified value or not lose by a margin greater than this value;</li>
        <li><b>asian handicap</b> ‚Äì Bet on the same handicap, but with quarter values (0.25 and 0.75), in which case the bet is divided into two equal parts (two adjacent to the selected value), and each of them is calculated separately.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These are just the basic types of bets. Be sure to familiarize yourself with each one so you understand what you're betting on, when it's best to use this type, and when it's best to give it up. When you realize that you have learned all the rules and understand when the bets play and when they do not, you can start betting.</p>
</div>

<div class="heads green">
    <h2>Types of bets and their designations</h2>
</div>
<div class="callout">
    <p>Here are the types of bets you can use:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Single Bets - there is only one event in the coupon;</li>
        <li><b>Multi Bet</b> ‚Äìthere are several events in the coupon, and the total odds are equal to the result of the multiplication of all events quotations;</li>
        <li><b>System Bet</b> ‚Äì in the coupon, too, several matches, depending on the chosen dimension a certain number of multi bets with the selected number of events (for example, 2/3 means 3 multi bets of 2 events each).</li>
        <li><b>Live</b> ‚Äìreal-time bets, i.e. on those matches that are going on right now.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Also available in this bookmaker's office are Lucky and Trixie bets <b>chain</b>, patent, contingent bets</p>
</div>

